name: typescriptcollectionsframework
author: Larry Diamond <ldiamond@ldiamond.com>
description: Collections Framework for TypeScript compatible with AngularJS

scripts.test: rm -r -f dist && gulp build && jasmine dist/spec/*.spec.js
scripts.typedocwin: typedoc --target ES5 --readme typedocreadme.html --gitRevision master  --excludeNotExported  --excludeExternals  --excludePrivate --out docs\typedoc\ src  --exclude **\spec\*.spec.ts --name "TypeScriptCollectionsFramework https://github.com/larrydiamond/typescriptcollectionsframework"
scripts.allwin: npm run testwin && npm run tslintwin && npm run tslintfixwin && npm run typedocwin
